data.description: New Construction in North Hall Schools on an awesome lot! Lot 2 features 1.65 acres and is a few miles away from Highway 365 to go North or South. The attached pictures reflect what floor plan will be built on this lot and examples of a finished product from this builder. This home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and comes in around 1400 Square feet. Lots 1 and 2 will have a shared road but own driveway, There will be an agreement drawn up for those shared road that leads to the driveways. Satellite based internet is available through Earthlink or Hughes Net. Finishes include LVP flooring throughout, upgraded base board package, soft close drawers, hardy plank siding, vinyl windows, granite countertops in kitchen and bathrooms, 386 square foot garage. Brand new home on a huge lot in North Hall! This home will be completed by the end of the year.
